From Brian Ceccarelli Subject Re Apr God's Promise in John In article Brian Kendig writes If you can explain to me why the death of Jesus was a good thing then I would be very glad to hear it and you might even convert Be warned however that I've heard all the most common arguments before and they just don't convince Be warned it is not my job to convert That is the job of the Holy And I frankly make a lousy I am only here to Your conversion is between you and I am out of the loop If you decide to follow Jesus of which I indeed would be estatic then all the glory be to Brian Ceccarelli